org.nlpcraft.model

Enum NCQueryState

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<NCQueryState>
      • org.nlpcraft.model.NCQueryState
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<NCQueryState>

    public enum NCQueryState
extends Enum<NCQueryState>
    This enumeration defines state of the query processing. It is passed to NCModel.onQueryState(NCQueryState, NCQueryContext, NCQueryResult, Throwable) query state callback method.

    • Enum Constant Summary

      Enum Constants 
      Enum Constant and Description
      QRY_BEFORE
      Query state just before the method NCModel.query(NCQueryContext) is called.
      QRY_ERROR
      Query state after query processing failed with unexpected exception.
      QRY_REJECTED
      Query state when query processing is finished with NCRejection exception.
      QRY_RESULT
      Query state after NCModel.query(NCQueryContext) method returned the result.
